                <h3><a href="/content/pij-statement-february-23-2020">PIJ statement, February 23, 2020</a></h3>        


<div class="field field-type-text-with-summary">
  
  
                <p>&ldquo;We are placing our hands on the trigger and we will avenge the blood of the martyrs by firing on Tel Aviv.&rdquo;<span class="footnote">Anna Ahronheim, &ldquo;Palestinian Islamic Jihad bombards South after clash near Gaza border,&rdquo; <em>Jerusalem Post</em>, February 24, 2020, <a href="https://www.jpost.com/Breaking-News/IDF-fires-mortar-shells-at-terrorists-in-southern-Gaza-Strip-report-618454">https://www.jpost.com/Breaking-News/IDF-fires-mortar-shells-at-terrorists-in-southern-Gaza-Strip-report-618454</a>.</span></p>        </div>
