      <div class="group-left columns large-2 medium-2 small-12">
      

<div class="field field-type-ds">
  
  
                <a href="/content/ziad-al-nakhalah-pij-secretary-general-january-5-2020"><img typeof="foaf:Image" src="https://www.counterextremism.com/sites/default/files/styles/medium/public/extremist_image/Ziyad%20al%20Nakhalah.jpg?itok=mRjBuTXN" width="" height="" alt="" /></a>        </div>
    </div>
  
      <div class="group-right columns large-10 medium-10 small-12">
      
                <h3><a href="/content/ziad-al-nakhalah-pij-secretary-general-january-5-2020">Ziad al-Nakhalah, PIJ secretary-general, January 5, 2020</a></h3>        


<div class="field field-type-text-with-summary">
  
  
                <p>The death of Quds Force commander Qasem Soleimani is a &ldquo;huge loss but at the same time he will be a model for all Muslims and free people in the world regarding how to confront America and the Zionist entity.&rdquo;<span class="footnote">dam Rasgon, &ldquo;Hamas, Islamic Jihad heads give condolences to Iran&rsquo;s FM on Soleimani&rsquo;s death,&rdquo; Times of Israel, January 5, 2020, <a href="https://www.timesofisrael.com/hamas-islamic-jihad-heads-give-condolences-to-irans-fm-on-soleimanis-death/">https://www.timesofisrael.com/hamas-islamic-jihad-heads-give-condolences-to-irans-fm-on-soleimanis-death/</a>.</span></p>        </div>
